{"tid":1464621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行出得黎既 就係一家人","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:50:23.000Z","uid":15136,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb734444a6addce577cef69e058c040fc3ddccd3","tid":1464621,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:15:45.000Z","msg":"一. 唔好兜口兜面屌佢，對屋企人唔該溫柔啲<br />\n<br />\n二. 拎手足既食物唔需要唔好意思，買得就係比你食既，就算唔要都比d反應人，唔洗啦唔該其實好易講<br />\n<br />\n三. 多d溝通，有禮貌，be humble<br />\n<br />\n四. 好多啲細佬妹驚巴士塞，坐機鐵入黎又一百，可能係成個星期零用，返到屋企又可能比老豆老母鬧，多啲關心下佢地，睇下有無需幫下手<br />\n<br />\n五. 仲細個班你地有需要即管出聲 唔洗怕羞 唔洗委屈 做大既有能力會幫你地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六. 齊上齊落 不分化 不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f65c2377d526ad02765ca2f1a8b896a8f0cd362","tid":1464621,"uid":15136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"準備開始十年自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ab8c115d3349c6ad3de0e06b87740c54fcd1eb","tid":1464621,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f65c2377d526ad02765ca2f1a8b896a8f0cd362","tid":1464621,"uid":15136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"準備開始十年自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"係十連自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3127b9ebd529e10c3521bdbc1428493df0a5feb1","tid":1464621,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:17:44.000Z","msg":"家規有無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3198afb5144a653911f2449b622510ebdc76309a","tid":1464621,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/da